            "secId": "s000015",
            "sentence": "In this section, we show that the Alternating Method  [3,9] can be easily adapted to design algorithms that determine whether integer solutions to (1.1) or (1.2) exist, and if so find one.",
            "startOffset": 308042,
            "title": "Alternating Method for integer solutions"
